parameters:
Someone wearing a hood suddenly came into the
classroom, captured Amelia-san, and left.

We tried to stop them too, but everyone was tired
from battling monsters...

No, Hiyo and the others aren't at fault. I wasn't
there either.

I felt a sinister atmosphere and couldn't move a
step.

Monsters suddenly appear, what on earth is
happening?

I don't understand either. But, I have to go help
Amelia.

Yes, that's right. I'm not confident in my magical
power, but I will go too.

I'm going too. I can't just stay silent when our
classmates are being abducted.
Do you know where they went?
I secretly followed them from behind.
I escaped before I was found out.
No, it's enough. With this, I can get Amelia back.

(There's no way it's just a coincidence... I
should have noticed sooner.)

(The room where Leviathan is, is for extracting
magical power.)

(Then it must be the student council president who
is monitoring.)
Where have you been until now?
Oh, I see. I apologize for my rudeness.

No, it's fine. Anyway, let's hurry to the club
room building.
